'''Samuel Ishimwe Karemangingo''' (wavutse 1991), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo mu [[Rwanda]] <ref>https://www.swissfilms.ch/en/person/samuel-ishimwe/A76E473A8D06475DA0944D06EB9622AB</ref>.  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ngufi ''Imfura i'', aho abaye umukinnyi wa mbere w’amafirime u [[Rwanda]] uhagarariye Berlinale<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/samuel-ishimwe/</ref>.  Usibye kuba umuyobozi, ni n'umukinnyi wa sinema, umwanditsi, injeniyeri y'amajwi, umwanditsi wa sinema na producer<ref>http://luxorafricanfilmfestival.com/en/PastEditions/2019/JuryMember/Samuel%20Ishimwe</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1991 i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]]. Nyina yamusize akiri uruhinja abura ababyeyi be n'umuryango we mugihe cya jenoside yo mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-43156718</ref>.  

== Umwuga ==
Nyuma yo kurangiza amashuri yisumbuye muri 2010, Ishimwe yatangiye gukora nkumunyamakuru nabafotora kuri 'igitekerezo.com'<ref>https://maishafilmlab.org/maisha-alumni/ishimwe-samuel/</ref>.  Mu mwaka wa 2011, yakoze filime ngufi ya mbere ''Paying debts'' yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://mubi.com/cast/samuel-ishimwe</ref>. Muri uwo mwaka, yitabiriye amahugurwa ya documentaire muri [[Uganda]] yakozwe na Maisha Film Lab. Igihe yari muri [[Uganda]], yakoraga nka producer wungirije kuri documentaire ngufi ''Invisible soul'' <ref>https://maishafilmlab.org/maisha-alumni/ishimwe-samuel/</ref>. Nyuma mu 2011, yitabiriye amahugurwa yerekanwe kuri firime yitwa 'K-dox' yakozwe na James Longley. Muri kamena 2012, Ishimwe yarangije amezi 3 yibanda cyane kubijyanye no gukina film muri Kwetu Film Institute. Hanyuma muri Nzeri 2012, yitabiriye gahunda yo kwandika no kuyobora yitwa 'A Sample of Work'.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/91983</ref> 

Yanditse inyandiko ya ''Crossing Line'' kandi yatsindiye igihembo mumarushanwa yo kwandika inyandiko yateguwe na Goethe Institut [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.goethe.de/ins/rw/en/m/kul/mag/21785115.html</ref>. Nyuma yaje gukora nk'umunyamakuru n'umufotozi nyuma yo kurangiza muri kaminuza nkuru y'u [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.ndangira.net/goethe-institut-kigali-independent-filmmaking-workshop/</ref>.  Hanyuma yagiye mu [[Busuwisi]] kugira ngo akomeze kwiga. Muri kamena 2017, Ishimwe yabonye impamyabumenyi ya firime muri Haute école d'art et de design (Ishuri ry’ubukorikori n’ubushakashatsi rya Geneve - UMUTWE).<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/73802</ref> 

Muri 2017, yakoze ''[[Imfura]]''  bisobanura ngo <nowiki>''First Born'</nowiki>. Iyi filime ivuga ku nkuru yashyizwe mu [[Rwanda]] nyuma ya jenoside.  Nibikorwa byambere byu [[Rwanda]] byashyizwe mumarushanwa ya Berlinale Short. Muri make yatsindiye igiciro cya silver Bear Jury Igiciro cya Berlin International Festival Festival<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/227343</ref><ref>http://luxorafricanfilmfestival.com/en/PastEditions/2019/JuryMember/Samuel%20Ishimwe</ref>.  

